 Question 1: Regional Sales Performance
Problem: Identify the top-performing Region based on total Sales. What is the percentage of total sales contributed by each region?

/*Total sales*/
SELECT
Sum (Sales)
FROM  ecommerce_sales_data;

Results:
Sum of sales :10667881
----------------------------------------------------------------
/*To compare the total sales of each region against the overall sales (%)*/
SELECT 
    Region, 
    SUM(Sales) AS Regional_Sales,
    ROUND(SUM(Sales) * 100.0 / (SELECT SUM(Sales) FROM ecommerce_sales_data), 2) AS Sales_Percentage
FROM ecommerce_sales_data
GROUP BY Region
ORDER BY Regional_Sales DESC;

